  ul
    li Start typing first and last name of the subscriber;
    li System will prompt full name when it matches exactly one user;
    li If there are no matching or there are more than one user matching - system will not prompt to select the user.

  h4 Search results
  ul
    li If there is a Subscriber selected, system will perform search only within documents user is subscribed to;
    li If there is no Subscriber selected, system will perform search within all documents;

